.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, funk, punk, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, cricket, swimming
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
4. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the fan of punk is between the fan of soul and the fan of funk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | punk           | soul | indie  |
| Sport         | badminton | swimming | soccer   | cricket |

