.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, pop, d&b, disco
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, skateboard, scooter, taxi
1. the fan of pop is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the fan of r&b is between the person driving the van and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | pop | r&b | d&b      |
| Transport     | scooter | van    | skateboard  | taxi |

