.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, cricket, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, scooter, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | rowing | baseball | cricket     | sailing   |
| Transport   | skateboard   | scooter     | bike | trike |

