.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, designer, manager, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, subway, jet-ski
1. the manager is between the person driving the helicopter and the photographer##2
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the photographer is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | designer | manager | photographer | engineer |
| Transport   | helicopter         | jet-ski       | trike    | subway         |

