.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pear, lime, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person eating pear and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | radish   | lime      | pear   | tomato  |
| Sport   | surfing | rowing | golf | soccer |

