.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, papaya, artichoke, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, horror, mystery, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person eating papaya is between the person eating pepper and the person eating garlic##2
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | garlic     | papaya | pepper   | artichoke        |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | mystery   | horror | sports |

