.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, magic-tricks, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, house, hip-hop, folk
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of house##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the fan of house is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | magic-tricks | cooking | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop          | house     | folk  | classical     |

