.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, project-manager, accountant, engineer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, horror, spy
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the engineer is between the person watching spy movies and the teacher##2
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | teacher | engineer | project-manager | accountant     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | horror    | spy   | crime |

