2. the argentine is the person driving the ship##1
3. the canadian is between the person driving the ship and the australian##2
4. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
