.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, german, indian
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, guinea-pig, bird
1. the american is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the indian is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the fish and the polish##2
4. the owner of the bird is the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | indian | polish | american | german |
| Pet           | guinea-pig  | bird  | hamster | fish      |

