The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, quad-bike, tram
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | photography | fishing | dancing | writing |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | motorbike  | tram    | quad-bike       |

