.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, argentine, colombian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting, badminton
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the japanese is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is between the indonesian and the colombian##2
5. the colombian is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | japanese   | indonesian   | argentine | colombian |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing | badminton     | weightlifting    |

