.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, traveling, hiking
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, rabbit, lizard
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | traveling    | hiking     | collecting | cooking |
| Pet     | horse | lizard | rabbit       | hedgehog     |

 